Conclusion: Based on the available data, there isn't immediate evidence suggesting that the domain 95photo.cn is malicious. However, due diligence would still involve verifying the legitimacy of the registrant email and conducting background checks on the registrar and name servers. It's important to note that absence of clear signs doesn't guarantee safety—it only suggests no obvious signs of malicious activity at this time.
